						<h1>Friends comparison - coming soon!</h1>
						<p>Soon we will be launching an exciting new feature which allows you to link rounds with your friends! If you've taken part in a round with your friends, and they have added their scores to {$domain.pagetitle}, you can link their scores with yours and view them side by side on the same chart. This adds a great element of sporting rivalry between you and your friends!</p>
