						<p class="bullet">Choose type of league or competition - knock-out, matchplay, traditional, etc.</p>
						<p class="bullet">Create round locations, time and date, select players or let {$domain.pagetitle} generate the draw.</p>
						<p class="bullet">Set-up entry fees and prizes for winning league or competitions.</p>
